That’s so funny!! I’m literally watching Glow Up right now. I’ve watched just 2 episodes and decided I was going to take a break a watch me some of my beauty guru’s before starting in on the next episode!! So funny to find that you’re a guest judge to something I was already beginning to watch.

I loved the 2nd episode show-off of using 5 products and nobody picked up the paint. The judges reaction where she said that they played it too safe and should have grabbed the paint and aggressively thrown it in the models face and then turn around and give the judges the bird. They would have respected that more. I was like, yes!!! Love that!!
